summary: An email from September 19, 2018, regarding the cancellation and rescheduling of an AOT TOC Briefing, which was to include updated proposals from AOT Team 4. The document is classified as UNCLASSIFIED and appears to be internal FBI or law enforcement communication.

events.title: Cancellation of AOT TOC Briefing
events.description: An AOT TOC Briefing scheduled for September 19, 2018, was canceled and will be rescheduled. AOT Team 4 was to present updated proposals.

keyFacts: The email is dated September 19, 2018, and is classified as UNCLASSIFIED.
An AOT TOC Briefing was canceled and will be rescheduled, with AOT Team 4 to present updated proposals.
The email appears to be internal FBI or law enforcement communication, as indicated by the subject line referencing FBI and the context of a briefing.
